<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Wolfein mechanoid drone -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_Drone.label>沃芬军用侦察无人机</Wolfein_Mechanoid_Drone.label>
  <!-- EN: A reconnaissance drone developed by the MegaCorp, constructed from parts sourced from the lowest-bidding departments. It features only basic patrol capabilities and a single low-powered laser gun. However, MegaCorp often deploys these drones in large numbers—when clustered together, they can still pose a considerable threat. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_Drone.description>军企旗下的侦察无人机，其零件均由招标出价最低的部门制造，仅具备基本的巡飞功能和一挺低功率激光枪。但军企通常习惯一次派出大量无人机进行侦察，它们若聚集起来仍然是个麻烦。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_Drone.description>
  <!-- EN: drone body -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_Drone.tools.drone_body.label>无人机体</Wolfein_Mechanoid_Drone.tools.drone_body.label>
  
  <!-- EN: Wolfein mechanoid armed drone -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_DroneArmed.label>沃芬军用武装无人机</Wolfein_Mechanoid_DroneArmed.label>
  <!-- EN: The armed drone equipped with dual rocket pods possesses high maneuverability and firepower coverage capability, enabling rapid deployment across various combat environments to execute suppression and clearance missions. -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_DroneArmed.description>配备双火箭巢的武装无人机，具备高机动性与火力覆盖能力，可快速部署于多种作战环境中，执行压制与清除任务。</Wolfein_Mechanoid_DroneArmed.description>
  <!-- EN: drone body -->
  <Wolfein_Mechanoid_DroneArmed.tools.drone_body.label>无人机体</Wolfein_Mechanoid_DroneArmed.tools.drone_body.label>
  
</LanguageData>